Sky Fighter Game Offline Version (Only 1MB)

INTRODUCTION
Sky Fighter is an html5 endless shooter game, get as much score as possible and beat the enemy aircraft!

HOW TO INSTALL?
1. Click "Add to Chrome" to install the extension
2. Pin the Sky Fighter extension icon to the Chrome toolbar
3. Click the Sky Fighter icon on the Chrome toolbar, the Sky Fighter popup will open. 
That's all you need to do! Have fun!

HOW TO PLAY?
Use your mouse to control the planes
